#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Basics:</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>ພື້ນຖານ:</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Do you want to go further?</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໄປຕໍ່ບໍ່?</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>Use case:</strong></span>"
msgstr "<span class=\"h1-fs\"><strong>ກໍລະນີການນຳໃຊ້:</strong></span>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>1. Flow 1:</strong> Most products need a human assessment as the "
"remaining quantity cannot be automatically computed. For those, a Recurring "
"Task is created in the Project App. This task reappears every week, and you "
"can personalize it with a checklist to avoid forgetting anything."
msgstr ""
"<strong>1. ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 1:</strong> ສິນຄ້າສ່ວນໃຫຍ່ຕ້ອງການການກວດສອບໂດຍມະນຸດ ເນື່ອງຈາກຈຳນວນທີ່ເ"
"ຫຼືອບໍ່ສາມາດຄິດໄລ່ໄດ້ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນ, ໜ້າວຽກທີ່ເກີດຂຶ້ນຊ້ຳ (Recurring Task) ຈະຖືກ"
"ສ້າງຂຶ້ນໃນແອັບໂຄງການ (Project App). ໜ້າວຽກນີ້ຈະປະກົດຂຶ້ນທຸກໆອາທິດ, ແລະ ທ່ານສາມາດປັບແຕ່ງມັນດ້ວຍ"
"ລາຍການກວດສອບ (checklist) ເພື່ອຫຼີກເວັ້ນການຫຼົງລືມສິ່ງໃດໜຶ່ງ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>2. Flow 2:</strong> For products that can be tracked, such as "
"bottled beers and sodas, you can use automated purchases. To try it, "
"navigate to your Point of Sale and sell a Blond Beer to a customer."
msgstr ""
"<strong>2. ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 2:</strong> ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າທີ່ສາມາດຕິດຕາມໄດ້ ເຊັ່ນ ເບຍຂວດ ແລະ ນ້ຳອັດລົມ, ທ່າ"
"ນສາມາດໃຊ້ການຊື້ອັດຕະໂນມັດໄດ້. ເພື່ອທົດລອງໃຊ້, ໃຫ້ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of Sale) ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ "
"ຂາຍເບຍ Blond Beer ໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Bar</span></strong><br/>"
msgstr "<strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">ບາ</span></strong><br/>"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website</font></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders directly in Odoo or go live with your \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">E-shop</font></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ເວັບໄຊ</font></strong> ທີ່ເປັນສ່ວນຕົວ ແລະ ຄົບ"
"ວົງຈອນໄດ້ຟຣີໃນບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດຄລິກ. ເລີ່ມຮັບຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ໂດຍກົງໃນ Odoo ຫຼື ເປີດໃຊ້ \n"
"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">ຮ້ານຄ້າອອນລາຍ "
"(E-shop)</font></strong> ຂອງທ່ານໃນບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດນາທີ."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model:product.template,name:bar_industry.product_product_31_product_template
msgid "Aperol"
msgstr "Aperol"

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As an administrator your pin is 3333. You can edit the pin of your employees"
" in the Employee App, in the Settings tab."
msgstr ""
"ໃນຖານະຜູ້ເບິ່ງແຍງລະບົບ ລະຫັດ pin ຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນ 3333. ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂລະຫັດ pin ຂອງພະນັກງານຂອງ"
"ທ່ານໄດ້ໃນແອັບພະນັກງານ (Employee App), ໃນແຖບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ (Settings)."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At the end of your service, remember to close your register. To do so, in "
"the Point of Sale App, select \"Close Register\" in the top-right menu. You "
"can then precise your cash amount and validate the closing."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອສິ້ນສຸດການບໍລິການຂອງທ່ານ, ຢ່າລືມປິດຮອບການຂາຍ. ເພື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໃນແອັບຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of "
"Sale App), ໃຫ້ເລືອກ \"ປິດຮອບການຂາຍ (Close Register)\" ໃນເມນູດ້ານຂວາເທິງ. ຈາກນັ້ນທ່ານສາ"
"ມາດລະບຸຈຳນວນເງິນສົດ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນການປິດ."

