"                        <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Social Media Marketing</font></strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">SMS Marketing</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການທຸກຊ່ອງທາງການສື່ສານຂອງທ່ານໃນບ່ອນດຽວດ້ວຍ Odoo <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານອີເມວ</font></strong>, <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານສື່ສັງຄົມອອນລາຍ</font></strong>, ແລະ <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">ການຕະຫຼາດຜ່ານ SMS</font></strong>."

#. module: bar_industry
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bar_industry.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
